      <title>特朗普外出时，在白宫附近被特勤局射击的武装男子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-09/authorities-armed-man-shot-by-secret-service-near-white-house-while-trump-out-of-town</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿（AP）＆Mdash;当局称，一名据信是从印第安纳州旅行的武装男子在周日凌晨在对抗之后被白宫附近的美国特勤局特工枪杀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-09/authorities-armed-man-shot-by-secret-service-near-white-house-while-trump-out-of-town</guid>
